@section Memory allocation tracing
@cindex mtrace

This file defines @code{mtrace()} and @code{muntrace()}, two functions which
enable and disable memory allocation tracing respectively.  These should be
called in matching pairs but will have no effect unless the @env{MALLOC_TRACE}
environment variable is set to the filename of the trace file to use.  The
resulting trace files can be processed by the @command{mtrace} perl script which
