The default delay is @samp{0}.

@cindex --free
@item @option{--free} <@var{colour}>
Specifies the colour to use for displaying free memory.  The default colour is
@samp{white}.

@cindex --height
@item @option{--height} <@var{size}>
Specifies the height (in pixels) of the drawing area.  The default height is
@samp{512}.

@cindex --internal
@item @option{--internal} <@var{colour}>
Specifies the colour to use for displaying internal heap memory.  The default
colour is @samp{red}.

@cindex --space
@item @option{--space} <@var{size}>
