format that the mpatrol library is being used with --- and don't forget to
include the version of the mpatrol library you are using!  Nowadays I only
use Windows XP and Interix or Cygwin on Intel x86 computers, so I will be most
likely unable to reproduce most of the system-specific bugs on other platforms.
A bug report that comes with an associated fix will be most welcome.

Enhancement requests and source code containing enhancements should also be sent
to @email{graemeroy@@users.sourceforge.net} or the mpatrol discussion group at
